FROM banking_new."Accounts" accounts
JOIN banking_new."Customers" customers ON accounts.customer_id = customers.customer_id
JOIN banking_new."Transactions" transactions ON accounts.account_id = transactions.account_id

FROM banking_new."Customers" customers
